    "summary": "CREATIVE BRAND CONSULTANT for CHANGEMAKERS  available for new projects  \n\nHi, I\u2019m Leoni, \nworking in the creative industry for 2 decades, specializing in doing the opposite.  \n\nI work with companies that need brand consults, creative strategies, or  impactful campaigns. Combining my superpower skills of creative research, design thinking, copywriting, creative direction, brand strategy, and culture change management, just to do one thing:\u00a0\n\u00a0\nBranding the Change!\u00a0\nto value people & purpose over profit\u00a0\n\u00a0\nYes, I strongly believe in the people that make your brand. Believe in change within. Use design research & design thinking to find your core, translating it into manifestos, brand positioning, strategic blueprints, impactful campaign concepts, creative direction, employer branding, and communication roadmaps. And above all, I make sure that you don't have a one-day statement on your wall, but real actions that speak! Yes, walking the talk.\n\nFurthermore, I\u2019m an author, orphan socks collector, a clumsy illustrator, read 11 books at a time, and have an excellent memory for totally unnecessary random things.\n\nCurious? Let\u2019s drink a coffee!\n\nwww.leonihuisman.com\nleoni@leonihuisman.com\n+31 6 125 224 93\n\n\nSkills: design thinking, creative direction, brand strategy, campaign concept, purpose branding, brand architecture, repositioning, employer branding, culture change management, transformation processes, creative sprint workshops\n\nAuthor: De capsulegarderobe \npublished by Meulenhoff\nA method to hack consumerism and buy less clothes. This book is for do-ers!",
